## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data and the inherent complexity of the issue. The effectiveness of proposed measures can vary significantly based on local contexts and implementation fidelity. Additionally, the divisive nature of gun control debates may hinder consensus on policy changes. Further research and longitudinal studies are needed to evaluate the long-term impact of these prevention strategies.

